---
layout: base.njk
title: Shot Okay Films — Every Frame Should Tell a Story
permalink: /
---
{% from "icons.njk" import serviceIcon %}

<div class="hero-outer">
  <div class="pgm-monitor">
    <div class="pgm-top">
      <span class="tally-dot on"></span>
      <span class="mono">PGM · LIVE</span>
      <span class="tc mono">00:00:00:00</span>
    </div>
    <div class="pgm-screen">
      <h1>Every frame should <span class="accent">tell a story.</span></h1>
      <p class="subhead">We shoot the ads, products, spaces, and faces your brand needs — one studio, six kinds of visual stories.</p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn-rec">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/{{ site.whatsapp }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tel-link">or WhatsApp us directly →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="waveform" id="waveform"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="wall-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow mono">VIDEO VILLAGE — MONITOR WALL</span>
    <h2>What we shoot</h2>
    <div class="wall-grid">
      {% for s in services.services %}
      <div class="monitor{% if loop.first %} active{% endif %}" data-id="{{ s.id }}" data-headline="{{ s.headline }}" data-desc="{{ s.description }}">
        <div class="mtop"><span class="tally-dot{% if loop.first %} on{% endif %}"></span><span class="mono">{{ s.cam }}</span><span class="tc mono">00:00:00:00</span></div>
        <div class="mscreen">{{ serviceIcon(s.icon) }}<span class="sname">{{ s.name }}</span></div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="wall-panel">
      <h3>{{ services.services[0].headline }}</h3>
      <p>{{ services.services[0].description }}</p>
      <a href="/contact/?service={{ services.services[0].name | urlencode }}" class="btn-rec">Quote this shoot</a>
    </div>
    <a href="/services/" class="view-all-link">→ View all services</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="wall-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow mono">SELECTED WORK</span>
    <h2>Featured projects</h2>
    <div class="portfolio-grid">
      {% for project in collections.projects | reverse %}
        {% if project.data.featured %}
        <div class="pf-card">
          <div class="pf-screen"><span class="pf-label mono">REEL</span></div>
          <div class="pf-meta"><span class="pf-name">{{ project.data.title }}</span><span class="pf-tag mono">{{ project.data.category }}</span></div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% else %}
        <div class="pf-card"><div class="pf-screen"><span class="pf-label mono">REEL 01</span></div><div class="pf-meta"><span class="pf-name">Commercial Ads</span><span class="pf-tag mono">Coming soon</span></div></div>
        <div class="pf-card"><div class="pf-screen"><span class="pf-label mono">REEL 02</span></div><div class="pf-meta"><span class="pf-name">Product Photography</span><span class="pf-tag mono">Coming soon</span></div></div>
        <div class="pf-card"><div class="pf-screen"><span class="pf-label mono">REEL 03</span></div><div class="pf-meta"><span class="pf-name">Real Estate Media</span><span class="pf-tag mono">Coming soon</span></div></div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <a href="/portfolio/" class="view-all-link">→ View full portfolio</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="notes-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="notes-grid">
      <div class="note">
        <span class="mono">CREW NOTE 01</span>
        <h3>One studio, every vertical</h3>
        <p>No juggling separate vendors for your ads, product shots, and real estate media — one team, one visual language.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="note">
        <span class="mono">CREW NOTE 02</span>
        <h3>Shot for the platform</h3>
        <p>Every frame is composed for how people actually watch it — feed, reel, listing, or storefront.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="note">
        <span class="mono">CREW NOTE 03</span>
        <h3>Direction, not just a camera</h3>
        <p>Concept, lighting, and story come built in — you get a finished look, not just raw footage.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-banner">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>Ready to shoot?</h2>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-rec">Get a Free Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
